<h1 style="margin-bottom: 30px;">Are Patient Billing Records Important During Medical Records Retrieval?</h1>
<div class="main_content_body">
	<p style="margin-bottom: 10px; font-family: 'Open Sans'; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic;">Nov 13 2014 | posted by Giles-Parscale</p>
	<!-- AddThis Button BEGIN -->
	<div class="addthis_toolbox addthis_default_style">
